<section class="education-intro">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="education-intro__row">
            <div class="education-intro__left-col">
                <div class="education-intro__bg">
                    <img src="img/education-intro.jpg" alt="" class="education-intro__bg-image">
                </div>
                <h1 class="education-intro__main-heading">
                    EDUCATION
                </h1>
                <div class="education-intro__main-text">
                    ISK aspires to provide students with a rigorous program that encourages them to excel not only in
                    their academic development but also in their personal growth.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="education-intro__right-col">
                <div class="education-intro__right-col-content">
                    <h2 class="education-intro__second-heading">
                        WHAT IS AN IB EDUCATION AT ISK?
                    </h2>
                    <div class="education-intro__second-heading-text">
                        <p>
                            Four main characteristics define an IB Education:

                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="education-intro__benefits">
                        <ol class="education-intro__benefits-list">
                            <li class="education-intro__benefits-list-item">
                                Centers on learners
                            </li>
                            <li class="education-intro__benefits-list-item">
                                Develops effective approaches to teaching and learning
                            </li>
                            <li class="education-intro__benefits-list-item">
                                Works within global contents
                            </li>
                            <li class="education-intro__benefits-list-item">
                                Explores significant content
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="education-intro__learn-more">
                    <a href="#" class="education-intro__learn-more-link">
                        Learn more about an IB Education
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="education-school">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="education-school__heading">
            IB SCHOOL
        </h2>
        <div class="education-school__slider js-education-school-slider">
            <div class="education-school__slider-wrapper">
                <div class="education-school__slider-arrows">
                    <button class="education-school__slider-arrow education-school__slider-arrow--prev">
                        <svg width="17" height="27" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-arrow-left">
                            <use xlink:href="#arrow-left"></use>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <button class="education-school__slider-arrow education-school__slider-arrow--next">
                        <svg width="17" height="27" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-arrow-right">
                            <use xlink:href="#arrow-right"></use>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="education-school__slider-main">
                    <div class="swiper-container">
                        <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                            <div class="swiper-slide">
                                <div class="education-school__slider-card">
                                    <div class="education-school__slider-card-image-wrapper">
                                        <img src="img/education-slider/1.jpg" alt=""
                                            class="education-school__slider-card-image">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="swiper-slide">
                                <div class="education-school__slider-card">
                                    <div class="education-school__slider-card-image-wrapper">
                                        <img src="img/education-slider/2.jpg" alt=""
                                            class="education-school__slider-card-image">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="swiper-slide">
                                <div class="education-school__slider-card">
                                    <div class="education-school__slider-card-image-wrapper">
                                        <img src="img/education-slider/1.jpg" alt=""
                                            class="education-school__slider-card-image">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="education-school__info">
            <div class="education-school__info-row">
                <div class="education-school__info-left-col">
                    <div class="education-school__large-text">
                        <p>
                            The International School of Kazan is an authorized International Baccalaureate (IB) World
                            School for the Primary Years Program, the Middle Years Program and the Diploma Program. * IB
                            World Schools are united in a common goal to provide a challenging and high-quality
                            education that fosters people who are internationally minded.

                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="education-school__info-right-col">
                    <div class="education-school__small-text">
                        <p>
                            *Only schools authorized by the International Baccalaureate can offer any of its four
                            academic programmes: the Primary Years Programme (PYP), the Middle Years Programme (MYP),
                            the Diploma Programme or the IB Career-related Certificate (IBCC). For further information
                            about the IB and its programmes, visit www.ibo.org.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


