                <div class="education-significant__text">
                    <p>
                        The curriculum is broad and balanced requiring students to study a range of disciplines.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Learning is concept-based. Information is not learned in isolation, but connected within and
                        across subject areas.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


